*mysql2-0.3.19 (31 Jul 2015)

  31 Jul 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +mysql2-0.3.19.ebuild:
  Version bump. Depend on virtual/libmysqlclient.

  07 Jun 2015; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add github to remote-id in metadata.xml

  27 Apr 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> mysql2-0.3.18.ebuild:
  Make sure mysql2 is recompiled when the virtual/mysql (sub)slot changes.

